Ideea de baza a acestui joc este urmatoarea: avem 2 jucatori, fiecare primeste 5 carti iar persoana care are cartile cat mai bune din punct de vedere al aranjamentelor, castiga. Aranjamentele sunt urmatoarele: carte mare, o pereche AABCD, doua perechi AABBC, trei bucati AAABC, chinta ABCDE consecutive, culoare ABCDE toate de aceeasi culoare, full house AABBB, chinta de culoare - aceasta este de forma ABCDE consecutive si cu aceeasi culoare, chinta roiala de forma ABCDE de aceeasi culoare dar sunt cartile maxime 10 J Q K A.
Programul consta in felul urmator: te intreaba cate persoane joaca poker, vor fi afisate cartile pentru fiecare persoana in parte, urmand sa mai fie inca o data afisate cartile pentru fiecare persoana insa de data aceasta aranjate iar la final, se va afisa un mesaj cu castigatorul si ce tip de aranjament a avut acesta.

The basic idea of this game is the following: we have 2 players, each receives 5 cards and the person who has the best cards in terms of arrangements wins. The arrangements are as follows: high card, one pair AABCD, two pairs AABBC, three pieces AAABC, consecutive straights ABCDE, suit ABCDE all of the same suit, full house AABBB, straight suit - this is of the form ABCDE consecutive and of the same suit, straight ABCDE-shaped queen of the same suit but the cards are 10 J Q K A.
The program consists of the following: it asks you how many people are playing poker, the cards for each person will be displayed, then the cards for each person will be displayed once again but this time arranged and at the end, a message will be displayed with the winner and what type of arrangement he had. 
